Phase 2c refactor pass
- Removed dead/unused code in src/shell/wallet.ts: baseOnlyMessage(), getUsdcBalance(),
  and the formatNeedsFundingMessage re-export (none referenced by any command or test).
- Simplified src/commands/music.ts, speech.ts, realface.ts: removed a redundant
  isPaymentRejectionError(msg) branch whose two arms were byte-identical (both called
  fail(msg, opts.json, { chain: getChain() })) — collapsed to one fail() call, dropped
  the now-unused isPaymentRejectionError import from those 3 files. video.ts keeps the
  check since its two branches genuinely differ (altModels hint on the non-payment path).
- File sizes all within the <800-line policy (largest: src/index.ts at 486 lines, which
  is the 18-subcommand commander wiring table — inherently repetitive declarative CLI
  registration, not duplication to collapse further without hurting readability).
